%spark
import org.apache.commons.io.IOUtils
import java.net.URL
import java.nio.charset.Charset
import org.apache.spark.sql.types._
import org.apache.spark.sql._
import org.apache.spark.sql.functions._
import spark.implicits._

case class CallSummaryAPI(
             call_sid: String,
             parent_call_sid: String,
             account_sid: String,
             parent_account_sid: String,
             start_time: String,
             end_time: String,
             duration: Int,
             connect_duration: Int,
             call_type: String,
             call_state: String,
             call_direction: String,
             disconnect_by: String,
             from: Participant,
             to: Participant,
             processing_state: String,
             pdd_ms: Int,
             tags: Seq[String],
             properties: ViProperties,
             carrier_edge: EdgeInfo,
             sip_edge: EdgeInfo,
             client_edge: EdgeInfo,
             sdk_edge: EdgeInfo
                     ) extends Serializable

case class Participant(
              caller: String,
              callee: String,
              carrier: String,
              connection: String,
              number_prefix: String,
              location: Location,
              city: String,
              country_code: String,
              country_subdivision: String,
              ip_address: String,
              sdk: TwilioSDK
                      )

case class EdgeInfo(
               properties: ViProperties,
               metrics: MetricsContainer,
               tags: Seq[String]
                   )

case class TwilioSDK(
                    sdk_type: String,
                    version: String,
                    platform: String,
                    region: String,
                    selected_region: String,
                    browser: Browser,
                    os: Os
                    )

case class Browser(name: String, major: String, version: String)
case class Os(name: String, version: String)

case class ViProperties(
               last_sip_response_num: Int,
               pdd_ms: Int,
               route_id: String,
               media_region: String,
               signaling_region: String,
               twilio_media_ip: String,
               twilio_signaling_ip: String,
               external_media_ip: String,
               external_signaling_ip: String,
               sip_call_id: String,
               user_agent: String,
               selected_region: String,
               region: String,
               trunk_sid: String,
               diconnectedBy: String
                       )

case class Location(
               lat: Float = 0.0f,
               lon: Float = 0.0f
                   )

case class MetricsContainer(
               inbound: Metric,
               outbound: Metric
                           )

case class Metric(
                 codec_name: String,
                 packets_received: Float,
                 packets_sent: Float,
                 packets_lost: Float,
                 packets_loss_percentage: Float,
                 jitter: Stats,
                 rtt: Stats,
                 mos: Stats,
                 audio_in: Stats,
                 audio_out: Stats,
                 latency: Stats,
                 codec: Int,
                 packet_delay_variation: PacketDelayVariation
                 )

case class Stats(
                min: Float,
                max: Float,
                avg: Float
                )

case class PacketDelayVariation(
                d50: Int,
                d70: Int,
                d90: Int,
                d120: Int,
                d150: Int,
                d200: Int,
                d300: Int)
             
val callSummary: Encoder[CallSummaryAPI] = Encoders.product[CallSummaryAPI]
val schema = callSummary.schema
val df = spark.read.schema(schema).parquet("hdfs://namenode:8020/voiceinsights/signal2019/data/signal-call-summary-small.parquet")
val table = df.createOrReplaceTempView("calls_api_v2")
// Total Rows
val totalRows = spark.sql("select count(call_sid) from calls_api_v2")
totalRows.show(false)

%md
# Business Intelligence Use Cases
 * Query to/from number_prefix, country_code & last_sip_response_num
 * Group By to/from number_prefix, country_code
 * Create a temporary view "model_dataset"

%spark
val modelDataset = spark.sql("SELECT from.number_prefix as caller_number_prefix, " + 
                             " from.country_code as caller_country_code," + 
                             " to.country_code as callee_country_code, " + 
                             " to.number_prefix as callee_number_prefix, " + 
                             " properties.last_sip_response_num as last_sip_response, " + 
                             " count(properties.last_sip_response_num) as counts " +
                             " FROM calls_api_v2 " + 
                             " WHERE carrier_edge IS NOT NULL " + 
                             " GROUP BY caller_number_prefix, " + 
                             " caller_country_code, " + 
                             " callee_country_code, " + 
                             " callee_number_prefix, " + 
                             " last_sip_response " + 
                             " ORDER BY counts desc")
modelDataset.createOrReplaceTempView("model_dataset")
modelDataset.show(100, false)

%sql
select * from model_dataset

%spark
val rows = spark.sql("SELECT call_sid," + 
                     " account_sid,  " + 
                     " parent_account_sid, " + 
                     " start_time, " + 
                     " end_time, " + 
                     " from.caller, " + 
                     " from.carrier as caller_carrier, " + 
                     " from.number_prefix as caller_number_prefix, " + 
                     " to.callee, " + 
                     " to.carrier as callee_carrier, " + 
                     " to.number_prefix as callee_number_prefix, " + 
                     " properties.last_sip_response_num as sip_response, " + 
                     " tags, connect_duration, " + 
                     " pdd_ms, " + 
                     " call_state " + 
                     " FROM calls_api_v2")
    .withColumn("end_time", to_timestamp(col("end_time")))
    .withColumn("year", year(col("end_time")))
    .withColumn("month", month(col("end_time")))
    .withColumn("day", dayofmonth(col("end_time")))
    .withColumn("hour", hour(col("end_time")))
    .cache 
rows.createOrReplaceTempView("call_summaries")
rows.show(false)

%sql
SELECT from.number_prefix as caller_number_prefix,
       to.number_prefix as callee_number_prefix, 
       properties.last_sip_response_num as last_sip_response, 
       count(properties.last_sip_response_num) as counts 
FROM calls_api_v2 
WHERE carrier_edge IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY caller_number_prefix, callee_number_prefix,  last_sip_response
ORDER BY counts desc

%md
# Call Summary Aggregation
   * Total Calls
   * Avg Connect Duration
   * Avg Post Dial Delay
   * Create Another Temp View "call_summary_aggregate"
   * Stacked graph AvgConnectDuration over AvgPddMs

%spark
 rows.groupBy($"account_sid")
     .agg(
        count("call_sid") as ("calls"),
        avg("connect_duration") as ("avg_connect_duration"),
        avg("pdd_ms") as ("avg_pdd_ms")
        )
        .orderBy(desc("calls"))
        .createOrReplaceTempView("call_summary_aggregate")

%sql
select * from call_summary_aggregate ORDER BY calls desc LIMIT 5

%md
# Client Projection

paragraphs.title: Client Projection
paragraphs.text:
%spark
val clientProjection = spark.sql("select * from calls_api_v2 where (to IS NOT NULL AND to.sdk IS NOT NULL) OR (from IS NOT NULL OR from.sdk IS NOT NULL)")
clientProjection.createOrReplaceTempView("client_projection")
clientProjection.show(false)

%spark
val client_metric_projection = spark.sql("select from.sdk.version as twilio_sdk_version, " +
                                         "from.sdk.platform as twilio_platform, "  +
                                         "from.sdk.browser.name as from_browser, "  +
                                         "from.sdk.browser.major as from_browser_major, " + 
                                         "sdk_edge.metrics.inbound.jitter.avg as inbound_avg_jitter, " +
                                         "sdk_edge.metrics.outbound.jitter.avg as outbound_avg_jitter "  +
                                         "FROM client_projection " +  
                                         "WHERE from IS NOT NULL AND from.sdk IS NOT NULL")
client_metric_projection.show(false)

%sql
select avg(inbound_avg_jitter) as avg_inbound_jitter,
       avg(outbound_avg_jitter) as avg_outbound_jitter ,
       twilio_platform,
       twilio_sdk_version
       from client_metric_projection 
       where twilio_platform IS NOT NULL
       group by twilio_platform, twilio_sdk_version
